name: Bold Stock Logos
description:
This set of original logos can be customised to fit your business.

When ordering please state which logo you would like (1-5) colour and wording (e.g. 'Your Business Name' will be replaced out for the name of your company)
All fonts, images and design will stay the same.

You will be emailed a PDF and JPEG of your chosen logo for use on stationery, website, print within 24-48 hours.

If you have more specific needs please contact us for custom business branding.
